License: MIT
Description: html-slacker
        ============
        
        Converts HTML to Slack formatted markdown
        
        Usage
        -----
        
        Install HTMLSlacker from pip.
        
        .. code:: bash
        
            $ pip install html-slacker
        
        Import library.
        
        .. code:: python
        
            >>> from htmlslacker import HTMLSlacker
        
        Use it.
        
        .. code:: python
        
            >>> HTMLSlacker('<b>Hello</b>, <i>Slack</i>!').get_output()
            '*Hello*,_Slack_!'
        
        Requirements
        ------------
        
        - Python >= 2.5
        - html
        
        Links
        -----
        
